cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper deals with efficient approximations to convolutional neural networks for image classification tasks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the accuracy and efficiency of the proposed method, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper evaluates its approach on the ImageNet dataset, which is a popular benchmark for computer vision tasks, and hence, it can also be categorized under multimedia (cs.MM).
